        assetName - the name of the .tflite model asset to load
        labels - the labels of the objects in the model

      • loadModelFromFile

        Parameters:
        absoluteFileName - the full path to the .tflite model file to load
        labels - the labels of the objects in the model

      • setClippingMargins

        void setClippingMargins(int left,
                        int top,
                        int right,
                        int bottom)
        Sets the number of pixels to obscure on the left, top, right, and bottom edges of each image passed to the TensorFlow object detector. The size of the images are not changed, but the pixels in the margins are colored black.
